des: Learn more about how Cashew can help your brand engage with Alexa users. This demo from Cashew.ai allows you to view a demo conversational ad on Alexa. To create the conversational ad, first visit the Cashew.ai site and follow the instructions there on how to create an conversation and then test it on Alexa using this skill.
